        <h2>9. References</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc2119">RFC 2119</a> - Key words for use in RFCs to Indicate Requirement Levels</li>
          <li><a href="/writing/relational-fidelity-metrics">Relational Fidelity Metrics</a> - Narrative companion to this specification</li>
          <li>PinchBench (pinchbench.com) - Agentic task completion benchmarks</li>
          <li>PersonaGym - Persona maintenance measurement across dialogue turns</li>
          <li>IETF AIGA (draft-2) - AI Agent Identity and Authorization</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

    </div>

